cule-rich systems, [HB89] 2351+456\nappears to be a ``vanilla'' HI 21 cm absorber.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 Aug 2004 23:44:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
