ge gap parameters, we are able to pursue the analysis of the\nphase diagram all the way up to such large values of Ms that there are no\nstrange quarks present.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 28 Aug 2004 03:03:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 31 Aug 2004 21:51:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-18"}
